<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Transaction Validated</title>
    <style>
        /* Add your custom CSS styles here */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        h1 {
            color: #333333;
        }
        p {
            color: #666666;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #0056b3;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Transaction Validated</h1>
        <p>Hello , My Name is {{ utilisateur.nom }} {{ utilisateur.prenom }}</p>
        <p>Your transaction has been successfully validated. Here are the details:</p>
        <p><strong>Transaction ID:</strong> {{ echangeProduit.id }}</p>
        <p><strong>Date:</strong> {{ echangeProduit.getDateEchange() | date('Y-m-d H:i:s') }}</p>
        <p><strong>Product Details:</strong> </p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Name:</strong> {{ echangeProduit.ProduitOut.titreProduit }}</li>
            <li><strong>Description:</strong> {{ echangeProduit.ProduitOut.descriptionProduit }}</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Thank you for the exchange !</p>
        <a href="{{ path('app_echange_produit_transactions') }}" class="button">View Transaction</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
